Broken Reed
results.description: Reed and Ben head for Stockholm to attend an international symposium of physicists, with Reed's friend Alyssa Moy; Crucible attacks; Reed notices a resemblance to Dr. Doom; Crucible steals Reed's rationality and mental talents for himself.

results.title: Tn the Eye of the Beholder
The Ever-Lovin', Blue-eyed End of the World
results.description: While relaxing after a hard night's work, The Thing begins to spawn many kinds of "Thing" duplicates.  Reed sends him to a pocket universe for eight hours so he can find a way to deal with them...and fast.

results.title: April is the Cruelest Month
results.description: Sue trains with Iron Fist and has a reunion with Namor; Reed takes Franklin to a baseball game, and takes Sue out to dinner; Alyssa worries about Reed; the Technet arrives with a warrant for Franklin's extradition to the Prime Continuum.

results.title: Seize the Child!
results.description: Alyssa and Franklin run from the Technet and the Warwolves, running into the the Bacchae in the process; the FF come to the rescue; Sue's heart's desire is revealed; the FF are transported to the Prime Continuum and face the entire Captain Britain Corps.
